icon = ExtResource("1_qty45")
packed_scene = ExtResource("3_d20d2")
goal_text = "\"Håkan Sunesson,\" the small and graying elderly man introduces himself. \"I have a problem that I believe your company could help solve.\"

\"We provide everything in bleeding-edge robotics under the sun,\" you boast confidently. \"Industrial, automotive, space, military, whatever you need.\"

\"Hamsters.\"

You blink at the earnest little man. \"...Hamsters?\"

\"Yes. My hamsters keep dying of old age. I want you to make robot hamsters for me.\"

Despite the substantial amount of money involved in the contract, morbid curiosity forces you to ask the question: \"Why?\"

Håkan returns your blank look. \"How else am I going to keep the hamster wheels spinning?\""
logic_type = 0
requirements = Array[ExtResource("4_d20d2")]([ExtResource("5_px5h4")])
